		"description": {
			"value": "<p>Wondrous Item - Rare (Requires Attunement)</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Buff</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Language:</strong> You know the Dwarvish language.</p></li><li><p><strong>Friend of Dwarvenkind:</strong> You have Advantage on &amp;reference[Persuasion] checks made to interact with dwarves and duergar.</p></li><li><p><strong>Toughness:</strong> - Your &amp;reference[Constitution] increases by 2, to a maximum of 20.</p></li><li><p><strong>Beard:</strong> At dawn each day, you have a [[/r 1d2]]{50% chance} of growing a full beard (if you can grow one) or a thicker beard (if you already have one).</p></li></ul><p><strong>Additional Benefits (if you are not a dwarf or duergar)</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Darkvision:</strong> You have Darkvision with a range of 60 feet.</p></li><li><p><strong>Resilience:</strong> You have Resistance to &amp;reference[Poison] damage, and Advantage on saving throws to avoid or end the &amp;reference[Poisoned] condition.</p></li></ul>",
